        </ul>

        <h2><span class="emoji">üîÄ</span> 5. Control Flow</h2>
        
        <h3>If / Else</h3>
        <pre>age = int(input("Enter your age: "))
if age >= 18:
    print("You are an adult.")
else:
    print("You are a minor.")</pre>

        <h3>Exercises</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Ask the user for a number and print if it is <strong>positive, negative, or zero</strong>.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Loops</h3>
        
        <h4>For Loop</h4>
        <pre>for i in range(5):
    print(i)</pre>

        <h4>While Loop</h4>
        <pre>count = 0
while count < 5:
    print(count)
    count += 1</pre>

